tion";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:663:"<p><img class="featured-image" src="https://ithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/small-sales-featured-540x305.jpg" />Pricing and sales can be a challenge for a lot of freelancers. We just want to do the work, and we dont want to get bogged down in how much to charge or the specifics of a sales process. But you can make a lot more money if you put some thought into those questions. [&#8230;]</p>
